title: New York String Orchestra
description: Experience the special 7 PM annual concert by the youthful New York String Orchestra. Enjoy the timeless majesty of an all-Mozart program, performed without intermission, conducted by Jaime Laredo and featuring clarinetist extraordinaire Ricardo Morales as soloist.
address: Stern Auditorium / Perelman Stage, Carnegie Hall, 57th and Seventh, New York, NY
